        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-06-26 17:10:05.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nThese jobs are failing in sandbox for reasons that seem to be related more to the sandbox itself:\n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/sandbox/job/sdc-dcae-d-master-csit-dcaed/\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/sandbox/job/sdc-dcae-d-master-verify-csit-dcaed/\n\nI'm reasonably confident the deepdiff version problem that prevents robotframework-onap installation and ultimately causes the build failure is not an issue in ONAP Jenkins (I will raise a ticket about the deepdiff version problem in sandbox tomorrow once we've taken a closer look at it with Daniel Rose) so I'm setting this ready for review.",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "5f40cf2d687a9830f6ad69ec15325410345c2a60",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 481,
          "name": "Jessica Wagantall",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "jwagantall@linuxfoundation.org",
          "username": "jwagantall"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-06-26 17:24:19.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nI could be wrong, but seems the issues cascade from dependencies not being pulled:\n07:42:42 Error response from daemon: manifest for nexus3.onap.org:10001/onap/dcae-dt:1.3-STAGING-latest not found\n\nAgain, we could try this in production and see..",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
