        "timestamp": "2019-06-27 08:16:31.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\ndcae-dt version issue is currently mostly cosmetic without any real effects on this CSIT (even though it still needs to be fixed so I raised https://jira.onap.org/browse/SDC-2396 for myself) and can not possibly be interfering with robotframework-onap dependencies. The dcae-dt image fails to download also in production, where deepdiff doesn't cause any problems (it is on version 3.3.0 instead of the 4.0.6 attempted in sandbox for some reason).\nHowever, these new jobs \nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/view/sdc-dcae-d/job/sdc-dcae-d-master-csit-dcaed/\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/view/sdc-dcae-d/job/sdc-dcae-d-master-verify-csit-dcaed/\n...now fail due to the already known problem with jinja version about which Daniel Rose should have already raised a ticket to LF?",
        "patchset_number": 4
      }
